name: WIDI
description: Backed by the Solana Foundation with first of its kind tools & apps (Overlimit Grantee). The first and only mobile-native AI-powered App on Solana. WIDI App lets you auto-copy top traders without hunting for wallets and tap into AI-powered pre-trade analysis. Trading Leaders set their rules and earn fees every time someone copy their trades. The governance token $WIDI unlocks app perks and Hedge Fund access.
